Vault of Satoshi is a [[exchange|currency_exchange]] that allows you to trade fiat currency to various crypto currencies (such as Bitcoin, Litecoin, Peercoin, and many more) with other members of the Exchange.

##Deposits

* Interac Online Deposits
* On-site Interac debit
* Vault of Satoshi Codes (created and redeemed from Vault of Satoshi)
* Bank Wire
* PAD (Pre-Authorized Debit)
* Online Bill Payment
* InstaBT

##Withdrawals

* Vault of Satoshi MasterCards
* Vault of Satoshi Interac Debit Cards
* Paypal
* EFT Bank Transfers

##History
The exchange was opened for public penetration testing in April 2013, and after extensive testing publicly on October 7th, 2013. 

* Vault of Satoshi is the [first exchange](http://www.coindesk.com/vault-satoshi-announces-proof-solvency-service/) in the world to use a 100% transparent audit using the open source software found [here](https://github.com/olalonde/proof-of-solvency).
* Vault of Satoshi was the first Canadian exchange to add Litecoin, Peercoin, Dogecoin, and many more. To date, it has the most extensive selection of CryptoCurrencies in Canada.

